   <title type="text">LIMEN: A Latin Teaching Portal</title>
   <content type="html"><![CDATA[<a href="http://indwellinglanguage.com/limen-a-latin-teaching-portal/">LIMEN: A Latin Teaching Portal</a><br /><blockquote class="tr_bq"><img alt="LIMEN - a Latin teaching portal" class="so-widget-image" height="147" src="http://indwellinglanguage.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/LIMEN-for-LIMEN-page-itself.png" style="display: block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; width: 100%;" width="400" /> </blockquote><div class="panel-grid-cell" id="pgc-2471-1-2"><div class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" id="panel-2471-1-2-0"><div class="textwidget"><blockquote class="tr_bq"><h1 style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-weight: normal;">Welcome to <em>LIMEN</em>!</span></span></h1><h6 style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-weight: normal;">Are you looking&nbsp;to teach Latin—not just <em>about</em> Latin—in a way that takes seriously what we know about language and the brain?</span></span></h6><h6 style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-weight: normal;">Getting started with this heroic, exhilarating work can be overwhelming.&nbsp;<em><a href="http://indwellinglanguage.com/limen-a-latin-teaching-portal#aboutthenamelimen">LIMEN</a></em>&nbsp;orients you to the many sources of support&nbsp;available to help you get (and keep) going!</span></span></h6><span style="font-size: small;">Click any title to view details of these four essentials.</span></blockquote></div></div></div><blockquote class="tr_bq"><div class="panel-grid-cell" id="pgc-2471-1-0">&nbsp;</div><div class="panel-grid-cell" id="pgc-2471-1-1"><div class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" id="panel-2471-1-1-0"><div class="textwidget"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/null" name="top"></a><a href="http://indwellinglanguage.com/limen-a-latin-teaching-portal#theory"><img alt="LIMEN theory" class="size-full wp-image-2599" height="79" src="http://indwellinglanguage.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/LIMEN-theory.png" width="201" /></a><br /><a href="http://indwellinglanguage.com/limen-a-latin-teaching-portal#practices"><img alt="LIMEN practices" class="size-full wp-image-2597" height="79" src="http://indwellinglanguage.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/LIMEN-practices.png" width="253" /></a><br /><a href="http://indwellinglanguage.com/limen-a-latin-teaching-portal#materials"><img alt="LIMEN materials" class="size-full wp-image-2596" height="79" src="http://indwellinglanguage.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/LIMEN-materials.png" width="266" /></a><br /><a href="http://indwellinglanguage.com/limen-a-latin-teaching-portal#resources"><img alt="LIMEN resources" class="size-full wp-image-2598" height="79" src="http://indwellinglanguage.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/LIMEN-resources.png" width="269" /></a><br /> </div></div></div></blockquote><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;">See AWOL's list of <a href="http://ancientworldonline.blogspot.com/2009/09/open-access-textbooks.html">Open Access Textbooks and Language Primers relating to the ancient world</a></span> </div>]]></content>
